name: bannercardcase
description:
the bannercardcases are similar in design to their paper cousins but are instead made out of street banner material! The kind of stuff you tend to see on the trendy city streets, and which tend to get discard after, have been skillfully hand crafted to become an item of worth - promising a high degree of durability, style and protection over your stuff.

the bannercardcases come in a wide range of one-of-a-kind designs and are on sale now at 20% off! The catch is that we'l be the ones hand picking your bannercardcase for you :)
We'l be in touch shortly after your purchase to find out roughly who the purchase is for, what his/her favourite colour is and we'l do our utmost to surprise you!

Sounds like fun?
Get yours now! :)

name: SUPRSCH Ltd Ed. Clutch 3 of 3
description:
Looking for a trusty, trendy companion to attack those late party nights with? The SUPRSCH has got your back.

name: PVC A4 Folder 2-5
description: Retaking PVC(Vinyl) Banners to the streets - the SUPRSCH PVC A4 Folder is handmade out of 100% genuine street banner material. Each component is carefully selected and positioned on the folder to ensure that you look SUPR cool carrying one. The PVC A4 folders are durable, lightweight and waterproof and can carry anything from A4 notepads, books, magazines and stationary.
